      .modal-content
            .modal-header
                  a(href='#').u-pull-right
                        span.icon X
                  .modal-title Insulin Sensitivity Factor
            .modal-body.m-0
                  p To Adjust your Insulin Sensitivity Factor throughout the day edit the below text. Time is in 24-hour format. 
                  p Use the below example as a reference 
                  textarea#EditIsf(style="min-height: 350px;")
                  pre
                        code.mb-1
                              |[
                              |	{
                              |		"Start":       "00h00m",
                              |		"End":         "05h59m",
                              |		"Sensitivity": 0.75
                              |	},
                              |	{
                              |		"Start":       "06h00m",
                              |		"End":         "23h59m",
                              |		"Sensitivity": 0.71
                              |	}
                              |]    
            .modal-footer.u-text-right
                  a(href="#").u-inline-block
                        input#SaveIsf(type="submit").btn-primary.pull-right